sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant ThemeScript as Theme Script
    participant MainJS as Main JS
    participant Components
    participant DataLayer as Data Layer
    participant DOMUtils as DOM Utils

    rect rgb(200, 220, 255)
    Note over Browser,ThemeScript: Phase 1: PRE-RENDER (Before Page Load)
    Browser->>ThemeScript: Read localStorage for theme
    activate ThemeScript
    ThemeScript-->>Browser: Apply data-theme to HTML
    deactivate ThemeScript
    end

    rect rgb(200, 255, 220)
    Note over User,Browser: Phase 2: INITIALIZATION
    User->>Browser: Request Page
    Browser->>MainJS: Fire DOMContentLoaded event
    activate MainJS
    MainJS->>Components: Execute component scripts
    activate Components
    Components-->>Browser: Inject SVGs and Layout
    deactivate Components
    MainJS->>Components: Sync Navigation Active Links
    activate Components
    Components-->>MainJS: Links synchronized
    deactivate Components
    MainJS->>Components: Sync Theme Toggle Icon UI
    activate Components
    Components-->>MainJS: UI synchronized
    deactivate Components
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 200)
    Note over MainJS,DOMUtils: Phase 3: DATA AND RENDERING
    MainJS->>DataLayer: Import dataset arrays
    activate DataLayer
    DataLayer-->>MainJS: Data loaded
    deactivate DataLayer
    MainJS->>DOMUtils: Pass Data and Template ID
    activate DOMUtils
    DOMUtils->>Browser: Locate template in DOM
    DOMUtils->>DOMUtils: Clone node and map data
    DOMUtils-->>Browser: Append elements to layout grid
    deactivate DOMUtils
    end

    rect rgb(255, 220, 220)
    Note over MainJS,Browser: Phase 4: BEHAVIOR AND INTERACTION
    MainJS->>Browser: Bind Theme Switcher events
    activate Browser
    Browser-->>MainJS: Event listeners attached
    deactivate Browser
    MainJS->>Browser: Setup ScrollSpy Observers
    activate Browser
    Browser-->>MainJS: Observers configured
    deactivate Browser
    MainJS->>Browser: Trigger ScrollReveal animations
    activate Browser
    Browser-->>MainJS: Animations started
    deactivate Browser
    deactivate MainJS
    end

    rect rgb(220, 240, 220)
    Note over User,Browser: Phase 5: READY STATE
    Browser-->>User: Page Ready for Interaction
    end
